Online slots and slot machines: types, device

Slot machines began to win the hearts of gamblers at the end of the 19th century. The first known instances of slot machines are Sittman and Pit and Liberty Bell. These rather primitive mechanical devices had three reels with symbols. After turning a special lever, the reels in the slots began to spin, and then stopped in a random order. The player received or did not receive a win depending on the location of the symbols. The complete unpredictability of all rotations was provided by a special internal mechanism.

The structure and transparency of online slots

More than 100 years have passed since the first slot machines appeared. And now online slots hardly resemble those gloomy machines. But the principle of their functioning has remained the same. The player starts the slot machine and combinations are randomly formed on the playing field. The randomness of all combinations and rotations is guaranteed by a special algorithm - RNG (RNG generator of random values). It is checked by independent authorities for transparency. And only after obtaining the necessary certificates and licenses, the game can be added to the portfolio of providers and the catalog of aggregators.
